title: Ep. 1285 - Baawri In Gada House - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baawri says she has come to seek forgiveness from Daya. Jetha tells her to forget all that happened and go home. Iyer asks Popatlal to propose Baawri as she is a good girl. Taarak reveals that Baawri is in love with Baga.

title: Ep. 1286 - Popatlal's Morning Dream - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya tells everyone that early morning dreams do come true and that's how she got married to Jethalal.

title: Ep. 1287 - Bhide Is Irritated - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide cribs about people not keeping the papers in an arranged way. He thinks of writing the thought for the day but can't find the chalk.

title: Ep. 1288 - Daya And Popatlal In A Bureau - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal asks the consultant about him being getting rejected every time.

title: Ep. 1289 - Bride Runs Away - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha, Nattu kaka, and Bagha hear about news where a girl has escaped from a marriage.

title: Ep. 1290 - Popatlal Finds Bulbul- Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal hears Bulbul praying to god that she gets married to someone of her choice. He tells her that it couldn't be a mere coincidence.

title: Ep. 1291 - Popatlal Being Lucky - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal spends time with Bulbul. Jetha asks Daya about today's visit to the bureau. Popatlal waits for the right moment to take Bulbul home.

title: Ep. 1292 - Daya Worries For Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya asks Jetha to call up Popatlal and ask his whereabouts. They went to look for him. Popatlal asks Bulbul to hide and to come only when he signals her.

title: Ep. 1293 - Police In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Police visit Gokuldham in search of Bulbul. Popatlal asks the police about their visit, the police inform that they have got information about Bulbul who has got married to someone in Gokuldham.

title: Ep. 1294 - Bulbul Hides - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal comes looking for Bulbul. Bulbul tells her how she she was hiding outside the window. He tells her not to repeat such stunts ever in life. Daya complains to Jetha about his increasing weight.

title: Ep. 1295 - Popatlal Denies To Help - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita asks Popatlal for help to which he denied. Jetha tells Babita if he could be of any help but Babita says only Popatlal help was needed. Popatlal goes shopping for his wife, Bulbul.

title: Ep. 1296 - Bulbul's Father In Town - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Police have been informed that Baldev Singh has reached Mumbai in search of his daughter.

title: Ep. 1297 - Tapu Sena Barges Into Popatlal's House - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena pays a visit to Popatlal. Tapu asks Popatlal for helping him out in an essay writing. He manages to shoo them away. Popatlal tells Bulbul to pack her bags and shift to somewhere else. Daya gives a head massage to Jetha.

title: Ep. 1298 - Champaklal Has A Doubt - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal waits for everyone to sleep so that he can escape from society. Champaklal notices a girl's shadow in Popatlal's house. He informs Daya and Jetha about the same. Champaklal thinks that she could be Bulbul.

title: Ep. 1299 - A Big Shock To Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya is angry with Popatlal as she believes that there is a girl in his house. Jetha wakes up Taarak and lets him know about Popatlal's secret.
